thread.title: Karen Kossow

author: Karen Kossow
title: Karen Kossow
text: I'd heard the founder of Munchery speak at a conference in San Francisco a few years ago and was looking forward to the day that they moved into the DC market. Well... they're here and I ordered my first meal yesterday. It arrived at the beginning of the delivery window, was yummy, and was pretty fairly priced. I enjoyed my first experience and as I don't enjoy cooking, look forward to ordering again in the future.
